        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Margaret!' said mr Hale, as he returned from showing his guest downstairs; 'I could not help watching your face with some anxiety, when mr Thornton made his confession of having been a shop boy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000000_000001",
