        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "I knew it all along from mr Bell; so I was aware of what was coming; but I half expected to see you get up and leave the room.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "I really liked that account of himself better than anything else he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'I am surprised at you, Margaret,' said her mother.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "I don't think, mr Hale, you have done quite right in introducing such a person to us without telling us what he had been.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "I really was very much afraid of showing him how much shocked I was at some parts of what he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "His father \"dying in miserable circumstances.\" Why it might have been in the workhouse.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "His father speculated wildly, failed, and then killed himself, because he could not bear the disgrace.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "No one came forwards to help the mother and this boy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "There was another child, I believe, a girl; too young to earn money, but of course she had to be kept.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "At least, no friend came forwards immediately, and mrs Thornton is not one, I fancy, to wait till tardy kindness comes to find her out.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "mr Bell said they absolutely lived upon water porridge for years-how, he did not know; but long after the creditors had given up hope of any payment of old mr Thornton's debts (if, indeed, they ever had hoped at all about it, after his suicide,) this young man returned to Milton, and went quietly round to each creditor, paying him the first instalment of the money owing to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000003_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000003_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Bell says), taking in mr Thornton as a kind of partner.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'How tainted?' asked her father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Oh, papa, by that testing everything by the standard of wealth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "When he spoke of the mechanical powers, he evidently looked upon them only as new ways of extending trade and making money.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "And the poor men around him-they were poor because they were vicious-out of the pale of his sympathies because they had not his iron nature, and the capabilities that it gives him for being rich.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Not vicious; he never said that.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Improvident and self indulgent were his words.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Margaret was collecting her mother's working materials, and preparing to go to bed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'And I do!' said her father laughing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Personally, as you call it, and all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "I don't set him up for a hero, or anything of that kind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "But good night, child.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Your mother looks sadly tired to night, Margaret.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Margaret had noticed her mother's jaded appearance with anxiety for some time past, and this remark of her father's sent her up to bed with a dim fear lying like a weight on her heart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "There were several other signs of something wrong about mrs Hale.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "But though she received caresses and fond words back again, in such profusion as would have gladdened her formerly, yet she felt that there was a secret withheld from her, and she believed it bore serious reference to her mother's health.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "She lay awake very long this night, planning how to lessen the evil influence of their Milton life on her mother.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Visiting register offices, seeing all manner of unlikely people, and very few in the least likely, absorbed Margaret's time and thoughts for several days.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000011_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000011_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "One afternoon she met Bessy Higgins in the street, and stopped to speak to her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Not exactly,' replied Margaret, smiling.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "At last she said in a low voice,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Bessy was silent in her turn for a minute or two.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'But what was it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'I had forgotten what I said for the time,' continued Margaret quietly. 'I should have thought of it again when I was less busy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "But Nicholas was not at home when they entered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "Margaret did not speak, but held the water to her lips.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Now, I'll not have my wench preached to.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'But surely,' said Margaret, facing round, 'you believe in what I said, that God gave her life, and ordered what kind of life it was to be?'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'I believe what I see, and no more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "That's my creed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000036_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000036_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "It's simple, and not far to fetch, nor hard to work.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1688_142285_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1688/142285/1688_142285_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1688",
        "content": "'Don't think hardly on him-he's a good man, he is.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
